auditorium

Class AuditoriumTemporalLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • auditorium.AAuditoriumLayer
      • auditorium.AuditoriumTemporalLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAuditoriumLayer

    public class AuditoriumTemporalLayer
extends AAuditoriumLayer
    This layer deals with temporality assertions in announcements. That is, it asserts which message or messages was or were previous to each message placed on the wire. This is where the entanglement happens.
